    "seo": {
      "title": "BMD Whole Body X-Ray Scan | Cadabams Diagnostics",
      "description": "Learn how a BMD whole body X-ray scan detects early bone loss, predicts fracture risk, and guides treatment—only at Cadabams Diagnostics.",
